%% wiki

YouTube Player
==============

Installation
------------

The YouTube Player is still under heavy development. You need to grab it from GitHub:

.. code-block:: bash

 $ git clone http://github.com/sbillaudelle/youtube-player.git
 $ cd youtube-player
 $ python youtube-player.py

