Ideas
-----
* display the video's rating (floating point)
* display the video's author/uploader
* implement subtitle displaying (``has_cc``, ``cc_*``, ``tts*``)
* display the video's upload date
* implement possibility to display the video's youtube.com URL and stream URLs
  for all resolutions/qualities
* what is ``fxep``?

Subtitles
~~~~~~~~~
* Note that there can be multiple subtitle tracks (different languages)
* ``cc_font`` recommends a font for the subtitle
* what is ``cc_asr`` and ``cc_load_policy``?
